UIC Alumni Association
Welcome to the UIC Alumni Association (UICAA). Since launching in 2017, UICAA focuses solely on UIC alumni and bringing our strong alumni network together to support common goals, such as UIC’s students and their success. Our volunteer UIC Alumni Board helps advance our goal of staying connected to our UIC alumni community that is more than 319,000 strong!






            UICAA Alumni Awards Nominations
          Heading link



 
Copy link



We are honored to award the highest alumni awards to UIC alumni. Nominations are now open. For more information, please click here. To view photos from past Alumni Awards Celebrations, click here.






            Connect With Us at UIC Alumni Exchange
          Heading link



 
Copy link












UIC alumni are doers, thinkers and knowers. We are carving big paths and using our voices for good. See for yourself at Alumni Exchange, a virtual event series connecting esteemed alumni and faculty.






            Join UIC Connected
          Heading link



 
Copy link












UIC Connected is an exclusive virtual network where you can connect with fellow alumni and current students for mentorship, networking and career growth. When you join, you can decide how you want to share career advice, build networks and help one another grow and connect. Access the platform at connected.uic.edu and view the Spanish version of the video here. For more info on the platform, consult this FAQ.





